nodes.text: Tino was a Human male who was a Rebel Elite Commando. He accompanied Leia, Chewbacca, Han Solo, and Luke Skywalker to Kiva on a mission to stop Project Starscream.

Tino trained with Rebel soldiers and became Rebel Elite Commando. On a mission to Kiva, he was in charge of baby-sitting Zak Arranda, Tash Arranda, and the baby, Eppon. He died when he was watching the small baby Eppon with his partner Bergan. When his superior Meex tried to find them, their bodies were gone.
